# Cursor Rules: Employee Compliance System

## Context & logic
- [cite_start]Always refer to `PRD 2 — Employee Management & Compliance System.pdf` for business rules[cite: 1].
- [cite_start]Enforce the 3-tier alert system: 60 days (Warning), 30 days (Urgent), 7 days (Final)[cite: 44].
- [cite_start]Required documents for "Compliant" status: Driver License, SSN, Work Permit, Alcohol Sales Permit, Food Safety Certificate[cite: 29, 30, 31, 32, 33].

## Tech Stack Preferences
- Frontend: Next.js 14 (App Router), Tailwind CSS, Lucide-react icons.
- Backend: Server Actions and API Routes following the `{ success: boolean, data: any, error: string }` pattern.
- [cite_start]Database: Use the schema defined in `DATABASE_SCHEMA.md`[cite: 63].

## UI/UX Standards
- Use a "Traffic Light" system for document status:
  - [cite_start]Red: Expired or Missing[cite: 49, 53].
  - [cite_start]Orange: Within the 60/30/7 day alert windows[cite: 44].
  - Green: Valid and outside alert windows.
- Sidebar must be Dark Theme (`bg-slate-900`), Main Content must be Light Theme (`bg-gray-50`).